Cynthia Lamontagne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cynthia_Lamontagne 0 Cynthia Ann LaMontagne (born February 15, 1966) is an American actress who has appeared in numerous television shows and films. She is best known for her recurring role as "Big Rhonda" in the fourth season of That '70s Show.
